    "description": "<p><strong>Planar Energy. </strong>Choose the type of&nbsp;planarite that serves as your primary life&nbsp;force from the following list: air, death,&nbsp;earth, fire, life, space, time, water. You&nbsp;gain resistance to a specific damage type&nbsp;based on this source.</p><p>Regardless of planarite type, the&nbsp;planar energy contained within allows you&nbsp;to forgo sleep. When you take a long rest,&nbsp;you spend 4 hours in a state of inactivity&nbsp;(instead of sleeping for 6 hours). While&nbsp;powered down in this way, you suffer no&nbsp;penalty to passive Perception. A long rest&nbsp;remains 8 hours for you as normal, and&nbsp;the remainder of the time must be filled&nbsp;only with light activity.</p><p><strong>TABLE: PLANARITE</strong></p><table style=\"width: 50%; border-width: 1px; height: 33.5938px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 46.0653%;\"><col style=\"width: 53.7428%;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\"><td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\"><h4><strong>Planarite</strong></h4></td><td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\"><h4><strong>Resistance</strong></h4></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\"><td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Air</td><td style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">Thunder</td></tr></tbody></table>",
